Well, you seem to be a STR-oriented Monk. That's fine if that's how you want to play the game, but I think most monks will tell you that they value HP and AC far more than STR for regular day-to-day grouping and soloing. Personally, I'd get rid of all that Pantherskin, Shiverback and especially that Helm of Rile and the STR ring (!) and get Acrylia Reinforced and other AC/HP items, but it's up to you... <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71792 target=_blank>Scalia</a> /  <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71783 target =_blank>Gluon</a> on E'ci</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udalarianwashere.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dalarian was here</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 79<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/19/02 11:41:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11486.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just some friendly advice needed.</span><hr size=1> You will have difficulty soloing if you overlook +hp items for +str items.<br>
<br>
My current spot, even though its mostly light blue now at 53 =/<br>
<br>
Just outside Acryllia Caverns in Grimling Forest.<br>
<br>
Benefits:<br>
<br>
Besides a few wandering SK's (ouch) all the target mobs are static, they don't run, and are all warriors. (!) Stay away from the ones that get buffed by the chanter mobs through a wall though heh.<br>
<br>
The loot they drop is entirely .01 weight stackable stuff that sells between 2-11~pp each piece, besides the odd FS~equivalent weapon.<br>
<br>
Very small aggro radius, I can run down past the where the wanderering SK's path (with SoW) and usually not aggro anything on the way down. Can usually fight the mobs at their spawn point, or easily pull singles to a clear spot.<br>
<br>
Bank and vendor in the same zone (Vah Shir faction), unfortunately no bandaids though. =/<br>
<br>
I have yet to see anyone else hunt there.<br>
<br>
<br>
Downsides:<br>
<br>
People make goodly sized trains running to Acrylia Caverns. Sometimes they then run the train around abit like they've never had a train on them before. Can be a pain to wait for everything to settle down.<br>
<br>
No bandages in the zone means running to Katta (not too bad) or SH (much further) to restock. Suggest stocking your bank with as many bandages as you have free slots and then using the bank to resupply. =p<br>
<br>
95% is light blue at 53. =/<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Other options:<br>
<br>
Another good area is Echo Caverns at the Taskmaster area, although the Taskmaster will probably give you problems, and it is almost always camped. The skeletons would be mostly blue at 52, or 50/50 worst case scenario (still alot of blues at 53).<br>
<br>
<br>
If I didn't hate Sol B, I'd be living there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=11486.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showNextMessage?topicID=11486.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11486.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.emailToFriend?topicID=11486.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.threadControl?topicID=11486.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11486.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11486.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="monklybusiness43508frm13">Board Rules<option value="monklybusiness43508frm17">Monk Change<option value="monklybusiness43508frm1">General<option value="monklybusiness43508frm16">New Features<option value="monk